text:
I didn't feel much hype for the game, even with that huge community and all the positive reviews. By now, I find it to be a good game, but very far away of being the best game ever. I guess it is because I don't find that the RPG-like mechanics did improve the genre by themselves. Actually I find the game to be a very poor RPG if you've ever considered that, while it's still a pretty solid "2D adventure/puzzle" game... ? Whatever, I don't really know how to name this genre.
OST is very nice and unique, though, specially nowadays.
